{"tid":2169399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食肆促資助五成租金半年","createTime":"2020-08-22T12:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T14:50:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"76f3eebeed78fde3ff5ca7f634a2d8a9b99eb244","tid":2169399,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/YIKFKFQE3NAQBNFWQDH6FAPYOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FYIKFKFQE3NAQBNFWQDH6FAPYOU%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6aof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=54bdc580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FYIKFKFQE3NAQBNFWQDH6FAPYOU%2F&h=a4eb02d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/YIKFKFQE3NAQBNFWQDH6FAPYOU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n食肆促資助五成租金半年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EPKzm7wZnNCAAV8QV3VmFFzOjYw=/5472x3648/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FDOWNEJ6N5C45G2Z4YKHPUTOTI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEPKzm7wZnNCAAV8QV3VmFFzOjYw%3D%2F5472x3648%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFDOWNEJ6N5C45G2Z4YKHPUTOTI.JPG&h=095623b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社區前進促政府為食肆小店設立第三輪抗疫基金。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港總商會發表問卷調查結果，顯示若政府不推出新一輪紓困措施 ，42%受訪中小企及24%大型企業認為業務最多只能支撐半年。調查亦發現，36%受訪公司營業額較疫潮前大跌至少一半，當中60%是中小企，大型企業佔29%。調查上周二至周六進行，共收回231份問卷，當中25%來自專業及商業服務業，15%來自貿易業。<br />\n<br />\n多間小店昨舉行記者會申訴，「阿媽靚湯」老闆劉先生擁四食肆，慨嘆疫潮。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一間聘用聾啞人士的籽果廚房負責人阿恩指，聾啞員工送外賣比一般人面對更多困難，餐。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育中心亦求補助<br />\n<br />\n補習社和教育中心同樣水深火熱，教育中心聯盟早前的問卷調查，獲1,758間教育中心回應，發現2月以來每間教育中心平均每月虧蝕近7萬元，當中租金支出佔虧蝕額達53%。聯盟認。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n食環署昨晚公佈修訂防疫抗疫基金下的餐飲處所資助計劃，將開放予符合申請資格但。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a1edd1a38778795dd3ce33d3202cc09db23580b3","tid":2169399,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"食肆連停業都未試過憑咩r 補貼<br />\n<br />\n連比人連環強制停業嗰堆鋪都未有補貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066c31b33107288c7bc7a9e34ed64e28c44408f4","tid":2169399,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"左手租右手，肥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0b681074aa114d5044b1f80dd8527b55ce5e25","tid":2169399,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"點解係食肆?<br />\n<br />\n全港都應該獲資助<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea95b6f1d38cf2e07796678f08a90fa733ff786e","tid":2169399,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"我反對魚蛋論<br />\n<br />\n我要全部行業都獲資助！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49755f198a5e026a30d04cbc012728efab0c0e03","tid":2169399,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"業主可以加租1倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c52fc832c236ddb05186ff481bba3b1d623abb","tid":2169399,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"業主仲唔即刻加租五成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfbd84b8ae51e13c04cb82a32a569b1e797a03e","tid":2169399,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"半年點夠起碼一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fb1cc1338369cd08febfebcb995f61861966ff","tid":2169399,"uid":134012,"like":0,"disl